Prerequisites


Build and open locally:

Need to have python2.7.9+ installed.
MangoDB server need to be installed and opened.

Install requirements for this project in a virtual environment.
    $ virtualenv --python=/usr/local/lib/python2.7.9/bin/python pybox
    # activate virtual environment
    $ source pybox/bin/activate
    # install requirements from requirements-pip
    $ pip install  -r requirements-pip


Use Docker to start project:

Install docker and docker-compose.
Build with 'sudo docker-compose build'
Start the container with 'sudo docker-compose up'

Use docker logs to see app logging.